<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_257979940cfb.aspx"><b>唐风·扬之水</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson257979940cfb">
<p>扬之水，白石凿凿。素衣朱襮，从子于沃。既见君子，云何不乐？<br />扬之水，白石皓皓。素衣朱绣，从子于鹄。既见君子，云何其忧？<br />扬之水，白石粼粼。我闻有命，不敢以告人。</p>
